---
// Footer Component
---

<footer id="contact" class="footer liquid-glass">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <h2 class="fade-in-up">Let's build something.</h2>
    <p class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">如果你也相信好的 AI 产品不只来自更强的模型，也来自更好的判断与体验设计，欢迎聊聊。</p>
    
    <div class="contact-links mt-md flex gap-sm fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
      <a href="mailto:your@email.com" class="pill liquid-glass btn">Email</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/arriettych" target="_blank" class="pill liquid-glass btn">GitHub</a>
      <a href="#" class="pill liquid-glass btn">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="#" class="pill liquid-glass btn">Resume</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="copyright mt-lg fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.3s;">
      © {new Date().getFullYear()} Arriettych. Designed with restraint.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    width: 100%; /* 通栏 */
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-glass-border);
  }

  .footer-inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    padding-left: var(--toc-width); /* 给左侧 TOC 留出视觉平衡，也可以不留 */
  }

  .footer h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: background var(--transition-fast), color var(--transition-fast), transform var(--transition-bounce);
  }

  .btn:hover {
    background: var(--color-text);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .contact-links {
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .copyright {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .footer-inner {
      padding-left: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
